    "collapsible_content_LHQB9a": {
      "type": "collapsible-content",
      "blocks": {
        "collapsible_tab_NTMyyD": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How long does the battery last on the Honiture X7?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>In standard mode, the X7 can run for up to 60 minutes. If you're cleaning a large area, it's recommended to have an<a href=\"https:\/\/honiture.com\/collections\/honiture-x7-vacuum-cleaner-accessories\/products\/honiture-x7-replacement-battery\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/honiture.com\/collections\/honiture-x7-vacuum-cleaner-accessories\/products\/honiture-x7-replacement-battery\"> extra battery<\/a>.<\/p>",
            "page": "",
            "custom_liquid": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_RD6wtM": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Is the Honiture X7 suitable for all floor types?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>Yes, the Vacuum X7 is designed to clean a variety of surfaces, including hardwood floors, carpets, and tiles.<\/p>",
            "page": "",
            "custom_liquid": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_NKNtDm": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How powerful is the suction power of the Honiture X7 vacuum cleaner?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>The X7 boasts a powerful 45 kPa suction force, perfect for collecting dust, hair, and particles, and is suitable for a variety of floor surfaces.<\/p>",
            "page": "",
            "custom_liquid": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_z4Ld4i": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Can I clean tight spaces and upholstery with the Honiture X7?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>Yes, the Cordless Vacuum Cleaner comes with a range of specialized attachments, including a crevice tool and upholstery brush, allowing you to clean tight spaces, furniture, and even car interiors with ease.<\/p>",
            "page": "",
            "custom_liquid": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_aFqTaA": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What kind of filtration system does the Honiture X7 use, and does it effectively filter out fine particles?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>Honiture X7 uses an advanced whole-machine <a href=\"https:\/\/honiture.com\/collections\/honiture-x7-vacuum-cleaner-accessories\/products\/honiture-x7-hepa-filters\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"honiture x7 hepa filters\">HEPA<\/a> filtration system. This system can capture more than 99.97% of fine particles such as dust, pollen and allergens.<\/p>",
            "page": "",
            "custom_liquid": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_aYeLJt": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How often should I replace the filter on vacuum X7?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>Brand recommendation: Most vacuum cleaner manufacturers recommend replacing HEPA filters <strong>every 6 to 12 months<\/strong>.<\/p>",
            "page": "",
            "custom_liquid": ""
          }
        }
